  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">GEF GOLD Mongolia-Philippines: Contribution Towards the Elimination of Mercury in the ASGM sector From Miners to Refiners</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1.Review of the policy and legal framework supporting formalization of the sector (UN Environment),2. Introduction of financing schemes allowing miners to adopt and subsequently investing in mercury-free technologies in a sustainable manner and access international gold markets more directly (UN Environment).,3. Upscale mercury-free technologies and support the development of health programmes for the ASGM sector (UNIDO).,4. Dissemination of information to ensure replication of the project activities in the participating countries and contributing to the global knowledge management platform established under global project of the GEF GOLD programme (UN Environment).,Project Management Cost,5. Monitoring and Evaluation</narrative>
  </description>
